更窄,并产生摩擦|**i在元音前<br>y在词首<br>il词末,并在元音后<br>ill在元音后**|<text class='green'>cahier</text> <text class='grey'></text> <br><text class='green'>yeux</text> <text class='grey'></text> <br><text class='green'>réveil</text> <text class='grey'></text> <br><text class='green'>travailler</text> <text class='grey'></text> |\n|<text class='red'>[p]</text>|上下唇紧闭,气流受阻后,突然冲出口腔|**p<br>pp**|<text class='green'>palais</text> <text class='grey'></text> <br><text class='green'>nappe</text> <text class='grey'></text> |\n|<text class='red'>[t]</text>|舌尖抵上齿,气流受阻后,突然冲出口腔|**t**|<text class='green'>tête</text> <text class='grey'></text> ; <text class='green'>site</text> <text class='grey'></text> |\n|<text class='red'>[k]</text>|舌尖抵下齿,舌后部抬起抵硬颚,<br>气流受阻后,突然冲出口腔|**c在a,o,u<br>及辅音字母前<br><br><br>qu<br>q<br>k**|<text class='green'>car</text> <text class='grey'></text> <br><text class='green'>comme</text> <text class='grey'></text> <br><text class='green'>culte</text> <text class='grey'></text> <br><text class='green'>classe</text> <text class='grey'></text> <br><text class='green'>quel</text> <text class='grey'></text> <br><text class='green'>cinq</text> <text class='grey'></text> <br><text class='green'>kaki</text> <text class='grey'></text> |\n|<text class='red'>[s]</text>|舌尖抵下门齿,上下牙床靠拢,<br>舌前部和硬颚之间形成窄缝,<br>气流通过时产生摩擦|**s不在两个元音字母间<br>c在e,i,y前<br>ç<br>x在少数词中**|<text class='green'>sel</text> <text class='grey'></text> <br><text class='green'>ceci</text> <text class='grey'></text> ; <text class='green'>cycle</text> <text class='grey'></text> <br><text class='green'>leçon</text> <text class='grey'></text> <br><text class='green'>six</text> <text class='grey'></text> |\n|<text class='red'>[l]</text>|舌尖抵上齿和齿龈,气流部分受阻,<br>从两边外出,声带振动|**l**|<text class='green'>lire</text> <text class='grey'></text> |\n|<text class='red'>[n]</text>|舌尖抵上齿和齿龈,软颚下降,<br>气流在口腔中完全受阻,由鼻腔发出,声带振动|**n**|<text class='green'>laine</text> <text class='grey'></text> |\n|<text class='red'>[f]</text>|上齿抵下唇,下唇略向内卷,<br>气流部分受阻,从上齿与下唇间擦出|**f<br>ph**|<text class='green'>foule</text> <text class='grey'></text> <br><text class='green'>photo</text> <text class='grey'></text> |\n|<text class='red'>[r]</text>|舌尖抵下齿,舌后部向软颚抬起,<br>小舌下垂,气流部分受阻,<br>气流通过时小舍略有颤动,并振动声带|**r**|<text class='green'>revue</text> <text class='grey'></text> <br><text class='green'>sur</text> <text class='grey'></text> |\n|<text class='red'>[∫]</text>|舌尖抬向上齿龈抵稍后部分,两者贴近,<br>气流部分受阻,由舌尖与上齿稍后部分擦出|**ch**|<text class='green'>cherche</text> <text class='grey'></text> <br><text class='green'>cacher</text> <text class='grey'></text> |\n|<text class='red'>[ʒ]</text>|发音方法同[∫],但声带振动|**j<br>g在e,i,y前**|<text class='green'>jeune</text> <text class='grey'></text> <br><text class='green'>gêne</text> <text class='grey'></text> ; <text class='green'>logis</text> <text class='grey'></text> |\n|<text class='red'>[b]</text>|发音方法同[p],但声带振动|**b**|<text class='green'>battre</text> <text class='grey'></text> |\n|<text class='red'>[v]</text>|发音方法同[f],但声带振动|**v<br>w**|<text class='green'>vie</text> <text class='grey'></text> <br><text class='green'>wagon</text> <text class='grey'></text> |\n|<text class='red'>[m]</text>|双唇闭拢,软颚下降,气流在口腔中完全受阻后,<br>由鼻腔发出,振动声带|**m**|<text class='green'>lame</text> <text class='grey'></text> <br><text class='green'>métal</text> <text class='grey'></text> |\n|<text class='red'>[d]</text>|发音方法同[t],但声带振动|**d**|<text class='green'>double</text> <text class='grey'></text> <br><text class='green'>raide</text> <text class='grey'></text> |\n|<text class='red'>[g]</text>|发音方法同[k],但声带振动|**g在a,o,u及<br>辅音字母前<br>gu在e,i前<br><br>gue**|<text class='green'>gare</text> <text class='grey'></text> <br><text class='green'>gomme</text> <text class='grey'></text> <br><text class='green'>guerre</text> <text class='grey'></text> <br><text class='green'>guide</text> <text class='grey'></text> <br><text class='green'>fugue</text> <text class='grey'></text> |\n|<text class='red'>[ɲ]</text>|舌尖抵下齿龈,舌面抬起接触硬颚形成阻塞,<br>气流从鼻腔发出|**gn**|<text class='green'>ligne</text> <text class='grey'></text> |\n|<text class='red'>[z]</text>|发音方法同[s],但声带振动|**z<br>s在两个元音字母中间<br>x在少数词中**|<text class='green'>zèle</text> <text class='grey'></text> <br><text class='green'>poser</text> <text class='grey'></text> <br><text class='green'>deuxième</text> <text class='grey'></text> | -->\n","link":"franch/phoneme","comments":true,"plink":"https://blog.vincenteliang.cn/franch/phoneme/","toc":[{"id":"原音","title":"原音","index":"1"},{"id":"辅音","title":"辅音","index":"2"}],"reward":true,"copyright":{"author":"Vincente Liang","link":"<a href=\"https://blog.vincenteliang.cn/franch/phoneme/\" title=\"音素与读音规则\">https://blog.vincenteliang.cn/franch/phoneme/</a>","license":"Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International (<a href=\\\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/\\\" rel=\\\"external nofollow\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)","published":"June 9, 2020","updated":"March 29, 2020"}}